Message: Hey guys, I am going to upload a series of three episodes where I’ll cover three new restaurants in town. PLEASE READ THE CAPTION AND SPREAD AWARENESS! We’re going through some really tough times. Its day 4 of self quarantine/social distancing. We have been maintaining social distance. We are not going out until or unless we really have to. We’re using masks and washing hands regularly. (Please use gloves too, I couldn’t find any in the pharmacies). We all know the precautions and what we have to do. 1. Cough or sneeze on your elbows 2. Wash hands regularly 3. Clean regularly used items 4. Don’t buy more than you need 5. Get rid of your clothes as soon as you reach home 6. Avoid spitting in public 7.Seek medical attention if you have fever, cough and sore throat. For Detailed information, https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/advice-for-public Please be careful and alert. and lets just do our parts to help the world get through this. Create awareness as much as you can. Tell your guards, maids and family about this ongoing issue. We have one simple job to do, we just have to stay home and do our part. Do share the latest facts and share the stories of people who have experienced the virus. Thats all it takes for now. Stay safe everyone. #covid_19 #maintainsocialdistance #corona #precautionsforcoronavirus

Hello Everyone! I am back with another video. In this video I accepted the challenge from Rafsan the ChotoBhai and cooked a meal for my mother! Checkout the whole video to find out my Mom’s review about my food! I made Shakshuka and garlic bread for my mother! Shakshuka is a popular Middle Eastern dish of eggs poached in spicy tomato and pepper sauce. It is ideal for breakfast although you can have it for lunch or dinner with bread or rice and it is a fairly healthy dish to eat. I have slightly changed the recipe to make it more appetizing for our Asian taste. রোজার মাস মানেই হালিম আর জিলাপি। আমি Personally হালিম বেশি পছন্দ করি। আজ Flavvora খাসির হালিমটা taste করলাম। মাংশর পরিমাণ যথেষ্ট ভালো ছিল। Last এত ভালো পরিমাণের মাংস পেয়েছিলাম Amarir হালিমে। ঘনত্ব ত দেখতেই পারছেন। আমার কাছে perfect লেগেছে! সবচাইতে ভালো লেগেছে তাদের ‘ তেতুলের টক ‘। আমি হালিম আর তেতুলের টক এর combination বেশ পছন্দ করি তাই এই ছোট্ট ব্যাপারটি আমার জন্য অনেক ভিন্নতা তৈরি করে। দাম অনুযায় পরিমাণ ভালো মনে হলো। ৪ জন এর খাসির হালিমের দাম ৮৫০ টাকা অর্ডার করতে চাইলে- https://www.facebook.com/flavvorabd/ This is not a sponsored post. I found this Halim tasty and good enough so I wanted to let you know.
